text: Marie-Charlotte Hebel (born 27 August 1984) was a French rugby union player. She played for the France women's national rugby union team at the 2006 Women's Rugby World Cup and 2010 Women's Rugby World Cup. == References == == Other websites == * https://www.world.rugby/photo/7950 Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:French rugby union players Category:Sportspeople from Nantes
